{"id":138839,"date":[{"year":1947,"month":3,"day":3}],"page":"8","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"新文艺","column":"","genre":"","count":"292","ytitle":"","mtitle":"自焚　“大赦”","ftitle":"","authors":["臧克家"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"臧克家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日前“大公报”“南罗通讯”:一农家青年，因抽丁中间，黑夜堆柴自焚死。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘着别人都睡了觉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘着鸡不叫，狗不咬；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人问的吉凶它们全不管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上的星星挂得那么高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天亲手打的柴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今夜，把它堆好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堆好了，坐到当中去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手里是火柴，心里是苦焦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“爸娘，儿子不孝了!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硬逼着去当兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死在自己家里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比死在战场上好”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第二天他被发现，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔夜的骨灰已经发寒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父母大哭，他们失掉了一个儿子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保长顿脚，他的这一名壮丁怎么去补足!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二月十三日下午。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"监狱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是地狱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地狱又小又黑暗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但，地狱里有地方安身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人管饭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出了监狱的大门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日月光明了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天地又广又辟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但，那儿去呢?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得到了自由，却失掉了生活!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三，十五日灯下"}]}